room_title: Escape room "Northfork Cabin" by Hidden Key Escape Games in Whitefish
room_description:
You volunteer to help the local Search and Rescue look for a number of hikers missing in the woods of the Northfork. The stories about these woods are creepy. Quite a number of hikers have gone missing recently, an old couple and some honeymooners.
As you search you discover a cabin in the woods. A storm is coming fast. Maybe the missing hikers are seeking shelter in the cabin? You decide to check it out and get out of the storm.
This cabin seems a bit off, maybe staying in the woods would have been a better choice?
